text: Toelgyfaloca is a genus of moths belonging to the subfamily Thyatirinae of the Drepanidae. ==Species== * Toelgyfaloca albogrisea (Mell, 1942) * Toelgyfaloca circumdata Houlbert, 1921 ==References== * , 2007, Esperiana Buchreihe zur Entomologie Band 13: 1-683 Category:Thyatirinae Category:Drepanidae genera
title: Toelgyfaloca
